  "detailed_description": "<strong>SHMUP Creator</strong> allows you to create and build your own shoot 'em up.<br>This tool is easy to use and powerful enough for more experienced users.<br>Thanks to the included assets you can start right away to have fun!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1289520/extras/cd3ca5d4b70f6695efd4879a93d7d22b.avif?t=1762020279\" width=610 height=72 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>\tTest your game anytime with the simple press of a button  <br></li><li>\tCreate 2D and 3D games<br></li><li>\tVertical, horizontal, or multi-directional levels<br></li><li>\tFree assets included: 3D models, sprites, sounds, music<br></li><li>\tImport your own sprites, 3D objects, and sounds</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1289520/extras/c7df4f3ff8568c438defd4d94c8392f2.avif?t=1762020279\" width=610 height=72 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>\tOptimized bullet engine: lasers, bullet patterns<br></li><li>\tExplosion editor</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1289520/extras/3add744d9f6b7881ea45ec1aa7296b9b.avif?t=1762020279\" width=610 height=72 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>\tCustomize everything with the mouse: no code, no scripts<br></li><li>\tEditors: gameplay, explosions, menu, HUD, level, enemies...<br></li><li>\tGameplay: scoring systems, gauges, chaining, medals, smart bombs, power-ups...</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1289520/extras/6e198fc9b7e20f4fb9ce0be70629576f.avif?t=1762020279\" width=610 height=72 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>\tExport your game as a stand-alone executable on <strong>Windows </strong>or <strong>Steam Deck</strong> and distribute it or sell it. No fee, no royalties!</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>SHMUP Creator</strong> allows you to create and build your own shoot 'em up.<br>This tool is easy to use and powerful enough for more experienced users.<br>Thanks to the included assets you can start right away to have fun!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1289520/extras/cd3ca5d4b70f6695efd4879a93d7d22b.avif?t=1762020279\" width=610 height=72 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>\tTest your game anytime with the simple press of a button  <br></li><li>\tCreate 2D and 3D games<br></li><li>\tVertical, horizontal, or multi-directional levels<br></li><li>\tFree assets included: 3D models, sprites, sounds, music<br></li><li>\tImport your own sprites, 3D objects, and sounds</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1289520/extras/c7df4f3ff8568c438defd4d94c8392f2.avif?t=1762020279\" width=610 height=72 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>\tOptimized bullet engine: lasers, bullet patterns<br></li><li>\tExplosion editor</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1289520/extras/3add744d9f6b7881ea45ec1aa7296b9b.avif?t=1762020279\" width=610 height=72 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>\tCustomize everything with the mouse: no code, no scripts<br></li><li>\tEditors: gameplay, explosions, menu, HUD, level, enemies...<br></li><li>\tGameplay: scoring systems, gauges, chaining, medals, smart bombs, power-ups...</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1289520/extras/6e198fc9b7e20f4fb9ce0be70629576f.avif?t=1762020279\" width=610 height=72 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>\tExport your game as a stand-alone executable on <strong>Windows </strong>or <strong>Steam Deck</strong> and distribute it or sell it. No fee, no royalties!</li></ul>",
